## Titlebar Buttons
Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize
Mouse 1 6 A Thumbnail
Mouse 1 1 A Exec rofi -theme .config/rofi/themes/promptmenu.rasi -show window
Mouse 1 3 A Exec scrot -d 2 'My_FVWM_%a-%d%b%y_%H.%M.png' -e 'viewnior ~/$f'
